text: Argema kuhnei is a moth in the family Saturniidae. It is found in the Democratic Republic of the Congo, Tanzania and Zambia.www.afromoths.net The larvae feed on Monotes katangensis. ==Subspecies== *A. kuhnei kuhnei Pinhey, 1969 *A. kuhnei katangensis Bouyer, 2008 (Democratic Republic of the Congo) ==References== Kuhnei Category:Moths described in 1969 Category:Moths of Africa
title: Argema kuhnei
